#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Editing Tools"
msgstr "Napredna orodja za urejanje"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment/Uncomment"
msgstr "Komentiraj/Odkomentiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Uncomment</"
"guimenuitem> commands, available from the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu "
"allow you to add or remove comment markers to the selection, or the current "
"line if no text is selected, if comments are supported by the format of the "
"text you are editing."
msgstr ""
"Ukaza <guimenuitem>Komentiraj</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Odkomentiraj</"
"guimenuitem>, ki sta na voljo v meniju <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu>, omogočata "
"dodajanje ali odstranjevanje označevalcev komentarjev izboru ali trenutni "
"vrstici, če ni besedilo je izbrano, če format besedila, ki ga urejate, "
"podpira komentarje."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rules for how commenting is done are defined in the syntax definitions, "
"so if syntax highlighting is not used, commenting/uncommenting is not "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Pravila za komentiranje so opredeljena v definicijah sintakse, tako da, če "
"označevanje sintakse ni uporabljeno, komentiranje/odkomentiranje ni mogoče."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some formats define single line comment markers, some multiline markers and "
"some both. If multiline markers are not available, commenting out a "
"selection that does not fully include its last line is not possible."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri formati določajo enovrstične oznake komentarjev, nekateri "
"večvrstične oznake, nekateri pa oboje. Če večvrstični označevalniki niso na "
"voljo, komentiranje izbora, ki ne vključuje v celoti zadnje vrstice, ni "
"mogoče."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a single line marker is available, commenting single lines is preferred "
"where applicable, as this helps to avoid problems with nested comments."
msgstr ""
"Če je na voljo oznaka ene vrstice, je zaželeno komentiranje posameznih "
"vrstic, kjer je to primerno, saj se tako izognete težavam z ugnezdenimi "
"komentarji."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When removing comment markers, no uncommented text should be selected. When "
"removing multiline comment markers from a selection, any whitespace outside "
"the comment markers is ignored."
msgstr ""
"Pri odstranjevanju označevalcev komentarjev ne sme biti izbrano "
"nekomentirano besedilo. Pri odstranjevanju oznak za večvrstične komentarje "
"iz izbora se vsak presledek zunaj oznak za komentarje prezre."

#. Tag: primary
#: advanced.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>comment</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>komentar</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To place comment markers, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or the "
"related keyboard shortcut sequence, the default is <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite postaviti oznake komentarjev, uporabite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali povezano zaporedje bližnjic na tipkovnici, privzeto je "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: primary
#: advanced.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>uncomment</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>odkomentiraj</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove comment markers, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uncomment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or the "
"related keyboard shortcut, the default is <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti oznake komentarjev, uporabite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odkomentiraj</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali povezano bližnjico na tipkovnici, privzeto je "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor Component Command Line"
msgstr "Ukazna vrstica komponente urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;'s editor component has an internal command line, allowing you to "
"perform various actions from a minimal &GUI;. The command line is a text "
"entry at the bottom of the editor area; to show it select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or use the shortcut (default is <keycombo action="
"\"simul\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo>). The editor provides a set of "
"commands as documented below, and additional commands can be provided by "
"plugins."
msgstr ""
"Komponenta urejevalnika &kappname; ima notranjo ukazno vrstico, ki vam "
"omogoča izvajanje različnih dejanj iz minimalnega &GUI;. Ukazna vrstica je "
"vnos besedila na dnu območja urejevalnika; za prikaz izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preklopi na ukazno "
"vrstico</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali uporabite bližnjico (privzeto je "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo>). Urejevalnik "
"ponuja nabor ukazov, kot je dokumentirano spodaj, dodatne ukaze pa lahko "
"zagotovijo vtičniki."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To execute a command, type the command then press the return key. The "
"command line will indicate whether it succeeded and possibly display a "
"message. If you entered the command line by pressing <keycap>F7</keycap> it "
"will automatically hide after a few seconds. To clear the message and enter "
"a new command, press <keycap>F7</keycap> again."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti ukaz, vnesite ukaz in pritisnite tipko return. V ukazni "
"vrstici bo prikazano, ali je uspelo, in morebiti prikazano sporočilo. Če ste "
"vstopili v ukazno vrstico s pritiskom <keycap>F7</keycap>, se bo po nekaj "
"sekundah samodejno skrila. Če želite počistiti sporočilo in vnesti nov ukaz, "
"znova pritisnite <keycap>F7</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command line has a built-in help system; issue the command "
"<command>help</command> to get started. To see a list of all available "
"commands issue <command>help list</command>; to view help for a specific "
"command, do <command>help <replaceable>command</replaceable></command>."
msgstr ""
"Ukazna vrstica ima vgrajen sistem pomoči; izdajte ukaz <command>pomoč</"
"command>, da začnete. Če si želite ogledati seznam vseh razpoložljivih "
"ukazov, izdajte <command>seznam pomoči</command>; če si želite ogledati "
"pomoč za določen ukaz, naredite <command>pomoč <replaceable>ukaz</"
"replaceable></command>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command line has a built in history, so you can reuse commands already "
"typed. To navigate the history, use the &Up; and &Down; keys. When showing "
"historical commands, the argument part of the command will be selected, "
"allowing you to easily overwrite the arguments."
msgstr ""
"Ukazna vrstica ima vgrajeno zgodovino, tako da lahko ponovno uporabite že "
"vnesene ukaze. Za krmarjenje po zgodovini uporabite &Up; in &Down; ključi. "
"Pri prikazu zgodovinskih ukazov bo izbran del ukaza z argumenti, kar vam "
"omogoča enostavno prepisovanje argumentov."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard Command Line Commands"
msgstr "Standardni ukazi ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Argument types"
msgstr "Vrste argumentov"

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "BOOLEAN"
msgstr "BOOLEAN"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used with commands that turns things on or off. Legal values are "
"<userinput>on</userinput>, <userinput>off</userinput>, <userinput>true</"
"userinput>, <userinput>false</userinput>, <userinput>1</userinput> or "
"<userinput>0</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja z ukazi, ki vklopijo ali izklopijo stvari. Pravne vrednosti "
"so <userinput>on</userinput>, <userinput>off</userinput>, <userinput>true</"
"userinput>, <userinput>false</userinput>, <userinput>1</userinput> ali "
"<userinput >0</userinput>."

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "INTEGER"
msgstr "INTEGER"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "An integer number."
msgstr "Celo število."

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "STRING"
msgstr "STRING"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A string, surrounded by single quotes (') or double quotes (\") when it "
"contains spaces."
msgstr ""
"Niz, obdan z enojnimi narekovaji (') ali dvojnimi narekovaji (\"), če "
"vsebuje presledke."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commands for Configuring the Editor"
msgstr "Ukazi za konfiguracijo urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands are provided by the editor component, and allow you to "
"configure the active document and view only. This is handy if you want to "
"use a setting different from the default settings, for example for "
"indentation."
msgstr ""
"Te ukaze zagotavlja komponenta urejevalnika in vam omogočajo, da "
"konfigurirate samo aktivni dokument in pogled. To je priročno, če želite "
"uporabiti nastavitev, ki se razlikuje od privzetih nastavitev, na primer za "
"zamik."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>set-tab-width</command><arg choice=\"req\">INTEGER width</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-širino-zavihka</command><arg choice=\"req\">INTEGER "
"širina</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the tab width to the number <userinput>width</userinput>."
msgstr "Nastavi širino zavihka na število <userinput>širina</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-indent-width</command><arg choice=\"req\">INTEGER width</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-širino-zamika</command><arg choice=\"req\">INTEGER "
"širine</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the indentation width to the number <userinput>width</userinput>. Used "
"only if you are indenting with spaces."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi širino zamika na število <userinput>širina</userinput>. Uporablja se "
"samo, če zamikate s presledki."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-word-wrap-column</command><arg choice=\"req\">INTEGER width</"
"arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-stolpec-za-prelom-besed</command><arg choice=\"req"
"\">INTEGER širina</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the line width for hard wrapping to <userinput>width</userinput>. This "
"is used if you are having your text wrapped automatically."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi širino črte za trdo previjanje na <userinput>širino</userinput>. To "
"se uporablja, če imate samodejno prelom besedila."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-icon-border</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavi-okvir-ikone</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN omogoči</"
"arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the visibility of the icon border."
msgstr "Nastavi vidnost obrobe ikone."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-folding-markers</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</"
"arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-zložljive-oznake</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the visibility of the folding markers pane."
msgstr "Nastavi vidnost podokna z zgibnimi oznakami."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-line-numbers</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-številke-vrstice</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the visibility of the line numbers pane."
msgstr "Nastavi vidnost podokna s številkami vrstic."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-replace-tabs</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavi-zamenjaj-zavihke</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, tabs are replaced with spaces as you type."
msgstr "Če je omogočeno, se tabulatorji med tipkanjem zamenjajo s presledki."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-remove-trailing-space</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-odstranite-končni-presledek</command><arg choice=\"req"
"\">BOOLEAN omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, trailing whitespace is removed whenever the cursor leaves a line."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, se končni presledek odstrani vsakič, ko kazalec zapusti "
"črto."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-show-tabs</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-prikaz-zavihkov</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, TAB characters and trailing whitespace will be visualized by a "
"small dot."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, bodo znaki TAB in presledki na koncu prikazani z majhno "
"piko."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-show-indent</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-prikaz-zamika</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, indentation will be visualized by a vertical dotted line."
msgstr "Če je omogočeno, bo zamik prikazan z navpično pikčasto črto."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-indent-spaces</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-presledke-za-zamike</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the editor will indent with <option>indent-width</option> spaces "
"for each indentation level, rather than with one TAB character."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, bo urejevalnik zamaknil s presledki <option>indent-width</"
"option> za vsako raven zamika namesto z enim znakom TAB."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-mixed-indent</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-mešani-zamik</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kappname; will use a mix of TAB and spaces for indentation. "
"Each indentation level will be <option>indent-width</option> wide, and more "
"indentation levels will be optimized to use as many TAB characters as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, &kappname; bo za zamik uporabil kombinacijo TAB in "
"presledkov. Vsaka raven zamika bo široka <option>širina-zamika</option>, več "
"ravni zamika pa bo optimiziranih za uporabo čim več znakov TAB."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When executed, this command will additionally set space indentation enabled, "
"and if the indent width is unspecified it will be set to half of the "
"<option>tab-width</option> for the document at the time of execution."
msgstr ""
"Ko se ta ukaz izvede, bo dodatno omogočen zamik presledka in če širina "
"zamika ni določena, bo nastavljena na polovico <option>širine zavihka</"
"option> za dokument v času izvajanja."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-word-wrap</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-prelom-besed</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"omogoči</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables dynamic word wrap according to <userinput>enable</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči dinamično prelivanje besed glede na <userinput>omogoči</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-replace-tabs-save</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable </"
"arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavi zamenjaj zavihke shrani</command><arg choice=\"req"
"\">BOOLEAN omogoči </arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, tabs will be replaced with whitespace whenever the document is "
"saved."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, bodo zavihki zamenjani s presledki vsakič, ko je dokument "
"shranjen."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-remove-trailing-space-save</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavitev-odstrani-končni-prostor-prihrani</command><arg choice="
"\"req\">Omogoči BOOLEAN</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, trailing space will be removed from each line whenever the "
"document is saved."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, bo končni presledek odstranjen iz vsake vrstice vsakič, ko "
"je dokument shranjen."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>set-indent-mode</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING name</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-način-zamika</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING ime</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the autoindentation mode to <userinput>name</userinput>. If "
"<userinput>name</userinput> is not known, the mode is set to 'none'. Valid "
"modes are 'none', 'normal', 'cstyle', 'haskell', 'lilypond', 'lisp', "
"'python', 'ruby' and 'xml'."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi način samodejnega zamika na <userinput>ime</userinput>. Če "
"<userinput>ime</userinput> ni znano, je način nastavljen na 'brez'. Veljavni "
"načini so 'none', 'normal', 'cstyle', 'haskell', 'lilypond', 'lisp', "
"'python', 'ruby' in 'xml'."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-auto-ident</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN script</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-samodejni-identifikator</command><arg choice=\"req"
"\">BOOLEAN skript</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable or disable autoindentation."
msgstr "Omogoči ali onemogoči samodejni zamik."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-highlight</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING highlight</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavite-poudarek</command><arg choice=\"req\">označba STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the syntax highlighting system for the document. The argument must be a "
"valid highlight name, as seen in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Highlighting</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu. This "
"command provides an autocompletion list for its argument."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi sistem označevanja sintakse za dokument. Argument mora biti veljavno "
"ime osvetlitve, kot je prikazano v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Označevanje</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Ta ukaz ponuja "
"seznam samodokončanja za svoj argument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reload all <link linkend=\"dev-scripting\">&javascript; scripts</link> used "
"by &kate;, including indenters and command line scripts."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naloži vse <link linkend=\"dev-scripting\">&javascript; skripti</"
"link>, ki jih uporablja &kate;, vključno z zamiki in skripti ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>set-mode</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING mode</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nastavljeni-način</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING način</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the filetype scheme for the current document."
msgstr "Izberite shemo vrste datoteke za trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>nn[oremap]</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING original</arg> <arg "
"choice=\"req\">STRING mapped</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>nn[oremap]</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING original</arg> <arg "
"choice=\"req\">STRING preslikan</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Map the key sequence <userinput>original</userinput> to <userinput>mapped</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Preslikaj zaporedje tipk <userinput>original</userinput> v "
"<userinput>preslikan</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commands for editing"
msgstr "Ukazi za urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "These commands modify the current document."
msgstr "Ti ukazi spremenijo trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indents the selected lines or the current line."
msgstr "Zamakne izbrane vrstice ali trenutno vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unindents the selected lines or current line."
msgstr "Razveljavi zamik izbranih vrstic ali trenutne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cleans up the indentation of the selected lines or current line according to "
"the indentation settings in the document."
msgstr ""
"Počisti zamik izbranih vrstic ali trenutne vrstice glede na nastavitve "
"zamika v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts comment markers to make the selection or selected lines or current "
"line a comment according to the text format as defined by the syntax "
"highlight definition for the document."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi označevalce komentarjev, da izbor ali izbrane vrstice ali trenutna "
"vrstica postanejo komentar v skladu z obliko besedila, kot je določeno z "
"definicijo poudarjanja sintakse za dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes comment markers from the selection or selected lines or current line "
"according to the text format as defined by the syntax highlight definition "
"for the document."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani označevalce komentarjev iz izbire ali izbranih vrstic ali trenutne "
"vrstice v skladu z obliko besedila, kot je določeno z definicijo poudarjanja "
"sintakse za dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the current line."
msgstr "Izbriše trenutno vrstico."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>replace</command><arg choice=\"req\"> STRING pattern</arg> <arg "
"choice=\"req\">STRING replacement</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>zamenjaj</command><arg choice=\"req\"> STRING vzorec</arg> <arg "
"choice=\"req\">STRING zamenjava</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replaces text matching <userinput>pattern</userinput> with "
"<userinput>replacement</userinput>. If you want to include whitespace in the "
"<userinput>pattern</userinput>, you must quote both the <userinput>pattern</"
"userinput> and <userinput>replacement</userinput> with single or double "
"quotes. If the arguments are unquoted, the first word is used as "
"<userinput>pattern</userinput> and the rest for <userinput>replacement</"
"userinput>. If <userinput>replacement</userinput> is empty, each occurrence "
"of <userinput>pattern</userinput> is removed."
msgstr ""
"Zamenja besedilo, ki se ujema z <userinput>vzorcem</userinput> z "
"<userinput>zamenjavo</userinput>. Če želite v <userinput>vzorec</userinput> "
"vključiti presledek, morate tako <userinput>vzorec</userinput> kot "
"<userinput>zamenjavo</userinput> dati v enojne ali dvojne narekovaje. Če "
"argumenti niso v narekovajih, se prva beseda uporabi kot <userinput>vzorec</"
"userinput>, ostala beseda pa za <userinput>zamenjava</userinput>. Če je "
"<userinput>zamenjava</userinput> prazna, je vsak pojav <userinput>vzorca</"
"userinput> odstranjen."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set flags to configure the search by adding a colon, followed by one "
"or more letters each representing a configuration, giving the form "
"<userinput>replace:options pattern replacement</userinput>. Available "
"options are:"
msgstr ""
"Zastavice lahko nastavite za konfiguracijo iskanja tako, da dodate dvopičje, "
"ki mu sledi ena ali več črk, od katerih vsaka predstavlja konfiguracijo, kar "
"daje obliko <userinput>zamenjaj: možnosti zamenjava vzorca</userinput>. "
"Razpoložljive možnosti so:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:322 advanced.docbook:715 advanced.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>b</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>b</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:323 advanced.docbook:716 advanced.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search backwards."
msgstr "Išči nazaj."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:327 advanced.docbook:720 advanced.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>c</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>c</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:328 advanced.docbook:721 advanced.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search from cursor position."
msgstr "Išči od položaja kazalca."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:332 advanced.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>e</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>e</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:333 advanced.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in the selection only."
msgstr "Išči samo v izboru."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:337 advanced.docbook:730 advanced.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>r</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>r</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:338 advanced.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do regular expression search. If set, you may use <userinput>\\N</userinput> "
"where N is a number to represent captures in the replacement string."
msgstr ""
"Izvedite iskanje po regularnem izrazu. Če je nastavljeno, lahko uporabite "
"<userinput>\\IN</userinput>, kjer je N število, ki predstavlja zajeme v "
"nadomestnem nizu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:344 advanced.docbook:737 advanced.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>s</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>s</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:345 advanced.docbook:738 advanced.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do case sensitive search."
msgstr "Iskanje razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>p</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>p</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prompt for permission to replace the next occurrence."
msgstr "Poziv za dovoljenje za zamenjavo naslednjega pojava."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:354 advanced.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>w</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>w</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:355 advanced.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match whole words only."
msgstr "Ujemaj samo cele besede."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>date</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING format</arg>"
msgstr "<command>datum</command><arg choice=\"req\">Oblika STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a date/time string as defined by the specified <userinput>format</"
"userinput>, or the format <quote>yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss</quote> if none is "
"specified. The following translations are done when interpreting "
"<userinput>format</userinput>:"
msgstr ""
"Vstavi niz datuma/časa, kot ga definira podani <userinput>format</"
"userinput>, ali format <quote>llll-MM-dd hh:mm:ss</quote>, če noben ni "
"določen. Pri interpretaciji <userinput>formata</userinput> se izvajajo "
"naslednji prevodi:"

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>d</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>d</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "The day as number without a leading zero (1-31)."
msgstr "Dan kot številka brez začetne ničle (1-31)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>dd</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>dd</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "The day as number with a leading zero (01-31)."
msgstr "Dan kot številka z ničlo na začetku (01-31)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>ddd</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>ddd</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "The abbreviated localized day name (&eg; 'Mon'..'Sun')."
msgstr "Skrajšano lokalizirano ime dneva (&eg; 'pon'..'ned')."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "dddd"
msgstr "dddd"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "The long localized day name (&eg; 'Monday'..'Sunday')."
msgstr "Dolgo lokalizirano ime dneva (&eg; 'ponedeljek'..'nedelja')."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>M</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>M</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "The month as number without a leading zero (1-12)."
msgstr "Mesec kot številka brez začetne ničle (1-12)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>MM</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>MM</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "The month as number with a leading zero (01-12)."
msgstr "Mesec kot številka z ničlo na začetku (01-12)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "MMMM"
msgstr "MMMM"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "The long localized month name (&eg; 'January'..'December')."
msgstr "Dolgo lokalizirano ime meseca (&eg; 'januar'..'december')."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>MMM</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>MMM</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "The abbreviated localized month name (&eg; 'Jan'..'Dec')."
msgstr "Skrajšano lokalizirano ime meseca (&eg; 'Jan'..'Dec')."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>yy</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>yy</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "The year as two digit number (00-99)."
msgstr "Leto kot dvomestno število (00-99)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "yyyy"
msgstr "yyyy"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "The year as four digit number (1752-8000)."
msgstr "Leto kot štirimestno število (1752-8000)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>h</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>h</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "The hour without a leading zero (0..23 or 1..12 if AM/PM display)."
msgstr "Ura brez vodilne ničle (0..23 ali 1..12, če je prikazan AM/PM)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>hh</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>hh</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "The hour with a leading zero (00..23 or 01..12 if AM/PM display)."
msgstr "Ura z vodilno ničlo (00..23 ali 01..12, če je prikazan AM/PM)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>m</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>m</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The minute without a leading zero (0..59)."
msgstr "Minuta brez vodilne ničle (0..59)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>mm</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>mm</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "The minute with a leading zero (00..59)."
msgstr "Minuta z vodilno ničlo (00..59)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>s</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>s</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "The second without a leading zero (0..59)."
msgstr "Druga brez vodilne ničle (0..59)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>ss</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>ss</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "The second with a leading zero (00..59)."
msgstr "Drugi z vodilno ničlo (00..59)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>z</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>z</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "The milliseconds without leading zeroes (0..999)."
msgstr "Milisekunde brez začetnih ničel (0..999)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>zzz</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>zzz</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "The milliseconds with leading zeroes (000..999)."
msgstr "Milisekunde z začetnimi ničlami ​​(000..999)."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>AP</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>AP</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use AM/PM display. AP will be replaced by either \"AM\" or \"PM\"."
msgstr "Uporabite prikaz AM/PM. AP bo nadomeščen z \"AM\" ali \"PM\"."

#. Tag: literal
#: advanced.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>ap</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>ap</literal>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use am/pm display. ap will be replaced by either \"am\" or \"pm\"."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite prikaz zjutraj/popoldne. ap bo nadomeščen z \"am\" ali \"pm\"."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>char</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING identifier</arg>"
msgstr "<command>char</command><arg choice=\"req\">identifikator STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command allows you to insert literal characters by their numerical "
"identifier, in decimal, octal or hexadecimal form. To use it launch the "
"Editing Command dialog and type <userinput>char: [number]</userinput> in the "
"entry box, then hit <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz vam omogoča vstavljanje dobesednih znakov glede na njihov numerični "
"identifikator v decimalni, osmiški ali šestnajstiški obliki. Če ga želite "
"uporabiti, odprite pogovorno okno Ukaz za urejanje in v polje za vnos "
"vnesite <userinput>char: [number]</userinput>, nato pritisnite <guibutton>V "
"redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>char</command> examples"
msgstr "<command>char</command> primeri"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Input: <userinput>char:234</userinput>"
msgstr "Vnos: <userinput>char:234</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output: <computeroutput>&#234;</computeroutput>"
msgstr "Izhod: <computeroutput>&#234;</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Input: <userinput>char:0x1234</userinput>"
msgstr "Vnos: <userinput>char:0x1234</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output: <computeroutput>&#x1234;</computeroutput>"
msgstr "Izhod: <computeroutput>in#x1234;</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: primary
#: advanced.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "replace, sed style"
msgstr "zamenjaj, slog sed"

#. Tag: secondary
#: advanced.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "search, sed style"
msgstr "iskanje, slog sed"

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>s///[ig]</command> <command>%s///[ig]</command>"
msgstr "<command>s///[ig]</command> <command>%s///[ig]</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command does a sed-like search/replace operation on the current line, "
"or on the whole file (<command>%s///</command>)."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz izvede operacijo iskanja/zamenjave, podobno sed-u, v trenutni "
"vrstici ali v celotni datoteki (<command>%s///</command>)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In short, the text is searched for text matching the <emphasis>search "
"pattern</emphasis>, the regular expression between the first and the second "
"slash, and when a match is found, the matching part of the text is replaced "
"with the expression between the second and last slash. Parentheses in the "
"search pattern create <emphasis>back references</emphasis>, that is the "
"command remembers which part of the string matched in the parentheses; these "
"strings can be reused in the replace pattern, referred to as <userinput>\\1</"
"userinput> for the first set of parentheses, <userinput>\\2</userinput> for "
"the second and so on."
msgstr ""
"Skratka, v besedilu se išče besedilo, ki se ujema z <emphasis>iskalnim "
"vzorcem</emphasis>, regularnim izrazom med prvo in drugo poševnico, in ko se "
"najde ujemanje, se ujemajoči del besedila nadomesti z izrazom med drugo in "
"zadnjo poševnico. Oklepaji v iskalnem vzorcu ustvarijo <emphasis>povratne "
"reference</emphasis>, to pomeni, da si ukaz zapomni, kateri del niza se "
"ujema v oklepajih; te nize je mogoče ponovno uporabiti v vzorcu zamenjave, "
"imenovanem <userinput>\\1</userinput> za prvi niz oklepajev, <userinput>\\2</"
"userinput> za drugega in tako naprej."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search for a literal <literal>(</literal> or <literal>)</literal>, you "
"need to <emphasis>escape</emphasis> it using a backslash character: "
"<userinput>\\(\\)</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati literal <literal>(</literal> ali <literal>)</literal>, ga "
"morate <emphasis>ubežati</emphasis> s poševnico nazaj: <userinput>\\(\\)</"
"userinput >"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you put an <userinput>i</userinput> at the end of the expression, the "
"matching will be case insensitive. If you put a <userinput>g</userinput> at "
"the end, all occurrences of the pattern will be replaced, otherwise only the "
"first occurrence is replaced."
msgstr ""
"Če na koncu izraza postavite <userinput>i</userinput>, ujemanje ne bo "
"razlikovalo med velikimi in malimi črkami. Če na koncu vstavite "
"<userinput>g</userinput>, bodo zamenjane vse pojavitve vzorca, sicer bo "
"zamenjana samo prva pojavitev."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replacing text in the current line"
msgstr "Zamenjava besedila v trenutni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your friendly compiler just stopped, telling you that the class "
"<classname>myClass</classname> mentioned in line 3902 in your source file is "
"not defined."
msgstr ""
"Vaš prijazen prevajalnik se je pravkar ustavil in vam povedal, da razred "
"<classname>myClass</classname>, omenjen v vrstici 3902 v vaši izvorni "
"datoteki, ni definiran."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&quot;Buckle!&quot; you think, it is of course <classname>MyClass</"
"classname>. You go to line 3902, and instead of trying to find the word in "
"the text, you launch the Editing Command Dialog, enter <userinput>s/myclass/"
"MyClass/i</userinput>, hit the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button, save the "
"file and compile &ndash; successfully without the error."
msgstr ""
"&quot;Zaponka!&quot; mislite, da je to seveda <classname>MyClass</"
"classname>. Pojdite v vrstico 3902 in namesto da bi poskušali najti besedo v "
"besedilu, zaženete pogovorno okno ukazov za urejanje, vnesete <userinput>s/"
"myclass/MyClass/i</userinput>, pritisnete <guibutton>OK</guibutton >, "
"shranite datoteko in prevedite &ndash; uspešno brez napake."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replacing text in the whole file"
msgstr "Zamenjava besedila v celotni datoteki"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Imagine that you have a file, in which you mention a <quote>Miss Jensen</"
"quote> several times, when someone comes in and tells you that she just got "
"married to <quote>Mr Jones</quote>. You want, of course, to replace each and "
"every occurrence of <quote>Miss Jensen</quote> with <quote>Ms Jones</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Predstavljajte si, da imate datoteko, v kateri večkrat omenjate "
"<quote>gospodično Jensen</quote>, ko pride nekdo in vam pove, da se je "
"pravkar poročila z <quote>gospodom Jonesom</quote>. Seveda želite vsako "
"ponovitev <quote>gdč. Jensen</quote> zamenjati z <quote>gdč. Jones</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the command line and issue the command <userinput>%s/Miss Jensen/Ms "
"Jones/</userinput> and hit return, you are done."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ukazno vrstico in izdajte ukaz <userinput>%s/Miss Jensen/Ms Jones/</"
"userinput> in pritisnite return, končali ste."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "A More Advanced Example"
msgstr "Naprednejši primer"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This example makes use of <emphasis>back references</emphasis> as well as a "
"<emphasis>character class</emphasis> (if you do not know what that is, "
"please refer to the related documentation mentioned below)."
msgstr ""
"Ta primer uporablja <emphasis>povratne reference</emphasis> kot tudi "
"<emphasis>razred znakov</emphasis> (če ne veste, kaj je to, si oglejte "
"povezano dokumentacijo, omenjeno spodaj)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suppose you have the following line:"
msgstr "Recimo, da imate naslednjo vrstico:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void MyClass::DoStringOps( String      &amp;foo, String &amp;bar, String *p, "
"int  &amp;a, int &amp;b )"
msgstr ""
"void MyClass::DoStringOps( String &amp;foo, String &amp;bar, String *p, int "
"&amp;a, int &amp;b )"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you realize that this is not nice code, and decide that you want to use "
"the <constant>const</constant> keyword for all <quote>address of</quote> "
"arguments, those characterized by the &amp; operator in front of the "
"argument name. You would also like to simplify the white space, so that "
"there is only 1 whitespace character between each word."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj se zavedate, da to ni lepa koda, in se odločite, da želite uporabiti "
"ključno besedo <constant>const</constant> za vse argumente <quote>naslov</"
"quote>, tiste, ki jih označuje &amp; operator pred imenom argumenta. Prav "
"tako bi želeli poenostaviti prazen prostor, tako da bo med vsako besedo samo "
"en presledek."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launch the Editing Command Dialog, and enter: <userinput>s/\\s+(\\w+)\\s"
"+(&amp;)/ const \\1 \\2/g</userinput> and hit the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button. The <userinput>g</userinput> at the end of the expression makes the "
"regular expression recompile for each match to save the "
"<emphasis>backreferences</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite pogovorno okno ukazov za urejanje in vnesite: <userinput>s/\\s+(\\w"
"+)\\s+(&amp;)/ const \\1 \\2/g</userinput> in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V "
"redu</guibutton> . <userinput>g</userinput> na koncu izraza povzroči, da se "
"regularni izraz znova prevede za vsako ujemanje, da se shranijo "
"<emphasis>povratne reference</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output: <computeroutput>void MyClass::DoStringOps( const String &amp;foo, "
"const String &amp;bar, String *p, const int &amp;a, const int &amp;b )</"
"computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"Izhod: <computeroutput>void MyClass::DoStringOps( const String &amp;foo, "
"const String &amp;bar, String *p, const int &amp;a, const int &amp;b )</"
"computeroutput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mission completed! Now, what happened? Well, we looked for some white space "
"(<literal>\\s+</literal>) followed by one or more alphabetic characters "
"(<literal>\\w+</literal>) followed by some more whitespace (<literal>\\s+</"
"literal>) followed by an ampersand, and in the process saved the alphabetic "
"chunk and the ampersand for reuse in the replace operation. Then we replaced "
"the matching part of our line with one whitespace followed by <quote>const</"
"quote> followed by one whitespace followed by our saved alphabetical chunk "
"(<literal>\\1</literal>) followed by one whitespace followed by our saved "
"ampersand (<literal>\\2</literal>)"
msgstr ""
"Misija končana! Zdaj, kaj se je zgodilo? No, iskali smo nekaj presledka "
"(<literal>\\s+</literal>), ki mu sledi ena ali več abecednih znakov "
"(<literal>\\w+</literal>), čemur sledi še nekaj presledka (<literal>\\s+</"
"literal>), ki mu sledi ampersand, in pri tem shranil abecedni kos in "
"ampersand za ponovno uporabo v operaciji zamenjave. Nato smo ujemajoči se "
"del naše vrstice zamenjali z enim presledkom, ki mu je sledil <quote>const</"
"quote>, ki mu je sledil en presledek, ki mu je sledil naš shranjeni abecedni "
"del (<literal>\\1</literal>), ki mu je sledil en presledek, ki mu je sledil "
"naš shranjen ampersand (<literal>\\2</literal>)"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now in some cases the alphabetical chunk was <quote>String</quote>, in some "
"<quote>int</quote>, so using the character class <literal>\\w</literal> and "
"the <literal>+</literal> quantifier proved a valuable asset."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je bil v nekaterih primerih abecedni kos <quote>String</quote>, v "
"nekaterih <quote>int</quote>, torej z uporabo razreda znakov <literal>\\w</"
"literal> in <literal>+</literal> kvantifikator se je izkazal za dragoceno "
"sredstvo."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorts the selected text or entire document."
msgstr "Razvrsti izbrano besedilo ali celoten dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort the selected lines or entire document naturally."
msgstr "Naravno razvrstite izbrane vrstice ali celoten dokument."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>sort</command> vs. <command>natsort</command>"
msgstr "<command>uredi</command> proti <command>naturedi</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>sort</command>(a10, a1, a2)</userinput> results in "
"<computeroutput>a1, a10, a2</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>uredi</command>(a10, a1, a2)</userinput> rezultira v "
"<computeroutput>a1, a10, a2</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>natsort</command>(a10, a1, a2)</userinput> results in "
"<computeroutput>a1, a2, a10</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>natsort</command>(a10, a1, a2)</userinput> povzroči "
"<computeroutput>a1, a2, a10</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected lines down."
msgstr "Premakni izbrane vrstice navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected lines up."
msgstr "Premakni izbrane vrstice navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove duplicated lines from the selected text or the whole document."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite podvojene vrstice iz izbranega besedila ali celotnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove trailing space from the selected text or the whole document."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite končni presledek iz izbranega besedila ali celotnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove leading space from the selected text or the whole document."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite začetni presledek iz izbranega besedila ali celotnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>join</command><arg choice=\"opt\">STRING separator</arg>"
msgstr "<command>združi</command><arg choice=\"opt\">Ločilo STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Join selected lines or whole document. Optionally takes a parameter defining "
"a separator, for example: <userinput><command>join</command> ', '</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Združi izbrane vrstice ali celoten dokument. Izbirno sprejme parameter, ki "
"določa ločilo, na primer: <userinput><command>join</command> ', '</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove all blank spaces from the selected text or the whole document."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite vse prazne prostore iz izbranega besedila ali celotnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command aligns lines in the selected block or whole document on the "
"column given by a regular expression given as an argument."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz poravna vrstice v izbranem bloku ali celotnem dokumentu na stolpec, "
"ki ga poda regularni izraz, podan kot argument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you give an empty pattern it will align on the first non-blank character "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"Če podate prazen vzorec, se bo privzeto poravnal s prvim znakom, ki ni "
"prazen."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "If the pattern has a capture it will indent on the captured match."
msgstr "Če ima vzorec zajem, se bo zajeto ujemanje zamaknilo."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: advanced.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>alignon -</userinput> will insert spaces before the first '-' of "
"each lines to align them all on the same column."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>alignon -</userinput> bo vstavil presledke pred prvi '-' vsake "
"vrstice, da jih vse poravna v isti stolpec."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>alignon :\\\\s+(.)</userinput> will insert spaces before the "
"first non-blank character that occurs after a colon to align them all on the "
"same column."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>alignon :\\\\s (.)</userinput> bo vstavil presledke pred prvi "
"neprazen znak, ki se pojavi za dvopičjem, da jih vse poravna v isti stolpec."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unwrap the selected text or the whole document."
msgstr "Odvijte izbrano besedilo ali celoten dokument."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>each</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING script</arg>"
msgstr "<command>vsak</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING skript</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Given a &javascript; function as an argument, call that for the list of "
"selected lines and replace them with the return value of that callback."
msgstr ""
"Glede na &javascript; funkcijo kot argument, pokličite to za seznam izbranih "
"vrstic in jih nadomestite s povratno vrednostjo tega povratnega klica."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Join selected lines"
msgstr "Združi izbrane vrstice"

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>each</command> 'function(lines){return lines.join(\", \")}'"
msgstr "<command>vsak</command> 'function(lines){return lines.join(\", \")}'"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:621 advanced.docbook:640 advanced.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Or, more briefly:"
msgstr "Ali bolj na kratko:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>each</command> 'lines.join(\", \")'"
msgstr "<command>vsak</command> 'lines.join(\", \")'"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>filter</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING script</arg>"
msgstr "<command>filter</command><arg choice=\"req\">Skript STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Given a &javascript; function as an argument, call that for the list of "
"selected lines and remove those where the callback returns false."
msgstr ""
"Glede na &javascript; funkcijo kot argument, pokličite to za seznam izbranih "
"vrstic in odstranite tiste, kjer povratni klic vrne false."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:636 advanced.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove blank lines"
msgstr "Odstranite prazne vrstice"

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>filter</command> 'function(1){return 1.length > 0;}'"
msgstr "<command>filter</command> 'function(1){return 1.length > 0;}'"

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>filter</command> 'line.length > 0'"
msgstr "<command>filter</command> 'line.length > 0'"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>map</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING script</arg>"
msgstr "<command>mapa</command><arg choice=\"req\">Skript STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Given a &javascript; function as an argument, call that for the list of "
"selected lines and replace the line with the value of the callback."
msgstr ""
"Glede na &javascript; funkcijo kot argument, jo pokličite za seznam izbranih "
"vrstic in zamenjajte vrstico z vrednostjo povratnega klica."

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>map</command> 'function(line){return line.replace(/^s+/,\"\");}'"
msgstr ""
"<command>mapa</command> 'function(line){return line.replace(/^s+/,\"\");}'"

#. Tag: userinput
#: advanced.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>map</command> 'line.replace(/^s+/,\"\")'"
msgstr "<command>mapa</command> 'line.replace(/^s+/,\"\")'"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicate the selected lines above the current selection."
msgstr "Podvoji izbrane vrstice nad trenutno izbiro."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicate the selected lines below the current selection."
msgstr "Podvoji izbrane vrstice pod trenutno izbiro."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commands for navigation"
msgstr "Ukazi za navigacijo"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>goto</command><arg choice=\"req\">INT line</arg>"
msgstr "<command>goto</command><arg choice=\"req\">INT line</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command navigates to the specified line."
msgstr "Ta ukaz vodi do navedene vrstice."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>grep</command> <arg choice=\"req\">STRING pattern</arg>"
msgstr "<command>grep</command> <arg choice=\"req\">STRING vzorec</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search the document for the regular expression <userinput>pattern</"
"userinput>. For more information, see <xref linkend=\"regular-expressions\"/"
">."
msgstr ""
"V dokumentu poiščite regularni izraz <userinput>vzorec</userinput>. Za več "
"informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"regular-expressions\"/>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>find</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING pattern</arg>"
msgstr "<command>najdi</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING vzorec</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command navigates to the first occurrence of <userinput>pattern</"
"userinput> according to the configuration. Following occurrences can be "
"found using <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (the default shortcut is <keycap>F3</keycap>)."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz se pomakne do prve pojavitve <userinput>vzorca</userinput> glede na "
"konfiguracijo. Naslednje pojavitve lahko najdete z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi naprej</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (privzeta bližnjica je <keycap>F3</keycap>)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The find command can be configured by appending a colon followed by one or "
"more options, the form is <userinput>find:options pattern</userinput>. The "
"following options are supported:"
msgstr ""
"Ukaz za iskanje je mogoče konfigurirati tako, da dodate dvopičje, ki mu "
"sledi ena ali več možnosti, oblika je <userinput>find:options pattern</"
"userinput>. Podprte so naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>ifind</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING pattern</arg>"
msgstr "<command>inajdi</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING vzorec</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command provides <quote>as-you-type</quote> searching. You can "
"configure the behavior of the search by appending a colon followed by one or "
"more options, like this: <userinput>ifind:options pattern</userinput>. "
"Allowed options are:"
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz omogoča iskanje <quote>med tipkanjem</quote>. Obnašanje iskanja "
"lahko konfigurirate tako, da dodate dvopičje, ki mu sledi ena ali več "
"možnosti, na primer: <userinput>ifind:options pattern</userinput>. Dovoljene "
"možnosti so:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do regular expression search."
msgstr "Izvedite iskanje po regularnem izrazu."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Commands for Basic Editor Functions (These depend on the application the "
"editor component is used in)"
msgstr ""
"Ukazi za osnovne funkcije urejevalnika (ti so odvisni od aplikacije, v "
"kateri se uporablja komponenta urejevalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the current document."
msgstr "Shranite trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save all currently open documents."
msgstr "Shrani vse trenutno odprte dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:805
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close the current document."
msgstr "Zapri trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close all open documents."
msgstr "Zapri vse odprte dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save and close the current document."
msgstr "Shranite in zaprite trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save and close all currently open documents."
msgstr "Shranite in zaprite vse trenutno odprte dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save and close the current document only if it has changed."
msgstr "Shrani in zapri trenutni dokument samo, če je bil spremenjen."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:831
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save and close all currently open documents only if they have changed."
msgstr ""
"Shranite in zaprite vse trenutno odprte dokumente le, če so bili spremenjeni."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous document in the documents list."
msgstr "Pojdite na prejšnji dokument na seznamu dokumentov."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next document in the documents list."
msgstr "Pojdite na naslednji dokument na seznamu dokumentov."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a new document in horizontal split view."
msgstr "Odprite nov dokument v horizontalno razdeljenem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a new document in vertical split view."
msgstr "Odprite nov dokument v navpičnem razdeljenem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:861
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload the current document if it has changed on disk."
msgstr "Znova naloži trenutni dokument, če se je spremenil na disku."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit a new document."
msgstr "Uredite nov dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the Print dialog to print the current document."
msgstr "Odprite pogovorno okno Natisni, da natisnete trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Code Folding"
msgstr "Uporaba zgibanja kode"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code folding allows you to hide parts of a document in the editor, making it "
"easier to overview large documents. In &kappname; the foldable regions are "
"calculated using rules defined in the syntax highlight definitions, and "
"therefore it is only available in some formats - typically program source "
"code, XML markup and similar. Most highlight definitions supporting code "
"folding also lets you manually define foldable regions, typically using the "
"<userinput>BEGIN</userinput> and <userinput>END</userinput> keywords."
msgstr ""
"Zgibanje kode vam omogoča, da skrijete dele dokumenta v urejevalniku, kar "
"olajša pregledovanje velikih dokumentov. V &kappname; prepogljiva območja so "
"izračunana z uporabo pravil, določenih v definicijah osvetlitve sintakse, "
"zato je na voljo le v nekaterih formatih - običajno izvorna koda programa, "
"oznaka XML in podobno. Večina definicij poudarkov, ki podpirajo zlaganje "
"kode, vam omogoča tudi ročno definiranje prepogljivih območij, običajno z "
"uporabo ključnih besed <userinput>BEGIN</userinput> in <userinput>END</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use the code folding feature, activate the folding markers using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item if they are not already visible. The "
"Folding Markers Pane on the left side of the screen displays a graphical "
"view of the foldable regions, with triangle symbols to indicate the possible "
"operation on a given region: a top down triangle means that the region is "
"expanded, clicking it will collapse the region and a right pointing triangle "
"will be displayed instead."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti funkcijo zgibanja kode, aktivirajte oznake za zlaganje z "
"menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"oznake za zlaganje</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, če še niso vidne. Podokno z "
"označevalniki za zlaganje na levi strani zaslona prikazuje grafični pogled "
"prepogljivih območij s trikotnimi simboli, ki označujejo možno delovanje na "
"danem območju: trikotnik zgoraj navzdol pomeni, da je območje razširjeno, s "
"klikom nanj se bo območje strnilo namesto tega bo prikazan desno usmerjen "
"trikotnik."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Three commands are provided to manipulate the state of folding regions, see "
"the <link linkend=\"view-code-folding\">menu documentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so trije ukazi za manipulacijo stanja zgibnih območij, glejte <link "
"linkend=\"view-code-folding\">dokumentacijo menija</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folded lines are remembered when a file is closed, so when you reopen "
"the file the folded nodes will still be folded. This applies to reload "
"operations as well."
msgstr ""
"Prepognjene črte se zapomnijo, ko je datoteka zaprta, tako da bodo "
"prepognjena vozlišča še vedno prepognjena, ko znova odprete datoteko. To "
"velja tudi za operacije ponovnega nalaganja."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want to use the code folding feature, you can disable the "
"<guilabel>Show folding markers (if available)</guilabel> option in the <link "
"linkend=\"appearance\">Appearance</link> page of the editor configuration."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite uporabljati funkcije zgibanja kode, lahko onemogočite možnost "
"<guilabel>Pokaži oznake za zlaganje (če so na voljo)</guilabel> na strani "
"<link linkend=\"appearance\">Videz</link> urejevalnika konfiguracijo."
